{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Demand reparations from the US for impact on the UK economy",
        "additional_details": "We believe the US Government must be held accountable for trying to drag NATO into supporting its attack on Iran and that the US has caused the passage of oil through the Strait of Hormuz to all but cease. We believe it is way beyond time for the UK Government to stand up to the US. The UK economy may take years to recover. We must therefore demand reparations from the USA.",
        "background": "Under the current US administration, western economies have been significantly impacted by unprecedented US tariffs, which have affected global markets. More recently, US attacks on Iran have caused an energy crisis. This directly impacts the cost of living in the UK.",
